<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Sentrax — Dashboard</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Rajdhani:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#0a0101;--bg2:#110202;--bg3:#1a0303;--bg4:#200404;
  --border:#2d0808;--border2:#3d1010;
  --red:#c0392b;--red2:#e74c3c;--red3:#ff6b6b;
  --red-dim:rgba(192,57,43,.12);--red-glow:rgba(231,76,60,.25);
  --tx:#f0e8e8;--tx2:#a08080;--tx3:#5a3535;--gold:#d4a843;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--tx);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 20% -10%,rgba(192,57,43,.08),transparent),radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 110%,rgba(192,57,43,.05),transparent);pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px}::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg2)}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--red);border-radius:2px}
.logo-text{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;letter-spacing:3px}
#landing{display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:100vh;position:relative;z-index:1}
.lnav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:rgba(10,1,1,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
.lnav-logo{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:28px;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--red2);text-shadow:0 0 20px var(--red-glow)}
.lnav-logo span{color:var(--tx);opacity:.4;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:2px;margin-left:4px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.lnav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px}
.lnav-link{color:var(--tx2);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color .2s}.lnav-link:hover{color:var(--tx)}
.lnav-btn{background:var(--red);color:#fff;padding:9px 22px;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s;border:1px solid var(--red2);font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif}.lnav-btn:hover{background:var(--red2);box-shadow:0 0 20px var(--red-glow)}
.hero{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:100px 24px 60px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero-grid{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(192,57,43,.04) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(192,57,43,.04) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px;mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 80% at 50% 50%,black,transparent)}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--red-dim);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:2px;padding:6px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--red3);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:28px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.hero-badge::before{content:'';width:6px;height:6px;background:var(--red2);border-radius:50%;animation:blink 1.5s infinite}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1;box-shadow:0 0 6px var(--red2)}50%{opacity:.3;box-shadow:none}}
.hero-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:clamp(60px,12vw,120px);line-height:.9;letter-spacing:6px;color:var(--tx);position:relative;z-index:1;margin-bottom:8px}
.hero-title .accent{color:var(--red2);text-shadow:0 0 40px var(--red-glow),0 0 80px rgba(192,57,43,.2)}
.hero-tm{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:18px;color:var(--tx3);vertical-align:super}
.hero-sub{color:var(--tx2);font-size:16px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.5px;max-width:520px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:36px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.hero-sub strong{color:var(--red3)}
.btn-hero{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:var(--red);color:#fff;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:3px;font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;transition:all .25s;border:1px solid var(--red2);position:relative;z-index:1}
.btn-hero:hover{background:var(--red2);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 30px var(--red-glow)}
.hero-stats{display:flex;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0;border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:60px;position:relative;z-index:1;width:100%;max-width:700px}
.hstat{flex:1;min-width:120px;padding:24px 20px;text-align:center;border-right:1px solid var(--border);position:relative}.hstat:last-child{border-right:none}
.hstat::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--red);opacity:0;transition:.3s}.hstat:hover::before{opacity:1}
.hstat-val{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:38px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--red2);line-height:1}
.hstat-lbl{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:4px}
.feats{padding:80px 32px;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;z-index:1}
.section-tag{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--red2);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}.section-tag::before{content:'//';opacity:.4}
.section-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,52px);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:6px}
.section-sub{color:var(--tx2);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:40px}
.feat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--border)}
.fc{background:var(--bg2);padding:28px;transition:all .2s;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.fc::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:3px;height:100%;background:var(--red);transform:scaleY(0);transform-origin:bottom;transition:.25s}.fc:hover{background:var(--bg3)}.fc:hover::after{transform:scaleY(1)}
.fc-ico{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:14px;display:block}
.fc-name{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--tx);margin-bottom:6px}
.fc-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.7;font-weight:500}
.lfooter{padding:20px 32px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.lfooter-logo{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--tx3)}
.lfooter-copy{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3);letter-spacing:1px}
#app{display:none;position:relative;z-index:1}
.sidebar{position:fixed;left:0;top:0;width:220px;height:100vh;background:var(--bg2);border-right:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;z-index:100;transition:transform .25s}
.sb-top{padding:20px 18px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.sb-logo{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--red2);text-shadow:0 0 15px var(--red-glow)}
.sb-logo-tm{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:2px}
.sb-server{padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;transition:.15s}.sb-server:hover{background:var(--bg3)}
.sb-server-icon{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--bg4);flex-shrink:0;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:14px;color:var(--red2);border:1px solid var(--border2)}
.sb-server-icon img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.sb-server-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;flex:1;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;letter-spacing:.5px}
.sb-server-arr{color:var(--tx3);font-size:10px}
.snav{padding:8px;flex:1;overflow-y:auto}
.snav-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:12px 10px 4px}
.ni{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:9px 10px;border-radius:2px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--tx2);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.5px;transition:all .15s;user-select:none;position:relative}
.ni:hover{background:var(--red-dim);color:var(--tx)}.ni.active{background:var(--red-dim);color:var(--red3)}.ni.active::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:2px;background:var(--red2)}
.ni-ico{font-size:14px;width:18px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0}
.sb-user{padding:10px 14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.sb-av{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--bg4);flex-shrink:0;border:1px solid var(--border2)}
.sb-uname{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;flex:1;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;letter-spacing:.5px}
.sb-out{background:none;border:none;color:var(--tx3);cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;padding:4px;transition:color .15s}.sb-out:hover{color:var(--red2)}
.main{margin-left:220px;min-height:100vh}
.topbar{height:50px;background:rgba(10,1,1,.95);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 22px;gap:10px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50}
.tb-crumb{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);letter-spacing:1px;flex:1}.tb-crumb span{color:var(--red2)}
.hamburger{display:none;background:none;border:none;color:var(--tx);cursor:pointer;padding:6px;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;margin-left:auto}.hamburger span{display:block;width:18px;height:2px;background:currentColor;border-radius:1px;transition:.2s}
.content{padding:24px;max-width:880px}
.page-section{display:none}
.page-header{margin-bottom:22px}
.page-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:36px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--tx);line-height:1}
.page-sub{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3);letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:4px}
#guild-picker{padding:24px;display:none}
.guilds-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:2px;background:var(--border);margin-top:20px}
.gc{background:var(--bg2);padding:20px 16px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.gc::before{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--red);transform:scaleX(0);transition:.2s}.gc:hover{background:var(--bg3)}.gc:hover::before{transform:scaleX(1)}
.gc-icon{width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:4px;margin:0 auto 10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:22px;color:var(--red2);background:var(--bg4);border:1px solid var(--border2);overflow:hidden}.gc-icon img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.gc-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px}
.gp-empty{color:var(--tx3);font-size:12px;padding:30px 0;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:1px}
.card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:2px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:14px;position:relative}.card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--red),transparent)}
.card-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--tx);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.card-hdr{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px}
.fr{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px}
.fg{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}
label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px}
input,select,textarea{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:2px;color:var(--tx);font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;padding:9px 12px;outline:none;transition:border-color .15s;width:100%}
input:focus,select:focus,textarea:focus{border-color:var(--red)}
select option{background:var(--bg3)}
.tr{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.tr:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.tr-lbl{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px}.tr-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);margin-top:2px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:.5px}
.tog{position:relative;width:38px;height:20px;flex-shrink:0}.tog input{opacity:0;width:0;height:0}
.tog-sl{position:absolute;cursor:pointer;inset:0;background:var(--bg4);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:10px;transition:.2s}.tog-sl::before{content:'';position:absolute;width:12px;height:12px;left:3px;top:3px;background:var(--tx3);border-radius:50%;transition:.2s}
.tog input:checked+.tog-sl{background:var(--red-dim);border-color:var(--red)}.tog input:checked+.tog-sl::before{transform:translateX(18px);background:var(--red2)}
.btn-save{background:var(--red);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:2px;padding:10px 22px;font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;margin-top:14px}
.btn-save:hover{background:var(--red2);box-shadow:0 4px 16px var(--red-glow)}
.sg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(130px,1fr));gap:2px;background:var(--border);margin-bottom:16px}
.sc{background:var(--bg2);padding:16px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.sc::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--red)}
.sc-lbl{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;margin-bottom:6px}
.sc-val{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:28px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--tx);line-height:1}
.info{background:var(--red-dim);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:2px;padding:10px 14px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--tx2);margin-bottom:14px;letter-spacing:.5px;border-left:3px solid var(--red)}
.pg2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
.pi{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.pi:nth-child(odd){border-right:1px solid var(--border)}
.pi-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.3px}.pi-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.wt{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px}
.wt th{text-align:left;padding:8px 10px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border2)}
.wt td{padding:9px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-weight:500}.wt tr:hover td{background:var(--red-dim)}
.badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:2px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.badge-eo{background:rgba(192,57,43,.2);color:var(--red3);border:1px solid rgba(192,57,43,.3)}
.badge-sa{background:rgba(212,168,67,.1);color:var(--gold);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,67,.2)}
.badge-tu{background:rgba(240,240,240,.05);color:var(--tx2);border:1px solid var(--border2)}
.pm-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.pm-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.pm-info{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.btn-rm{background:rgba(192,57,43,.1);border:1px solid rgba(192,57,43,.2);color:var(--red2);border-radius:2px;padding:3px 10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;cursor:pointer;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;transition:all .15s;text-transform:uppercase}.btn-rm:hover{background:rgba(192,57,43,.25)}
.add-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr auto;gap:10px;margin-top:14px;align-items:end}
.slide-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.6);z-index:200;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .25s}.slide-overlay.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
.slide-panel{position:fixed;top:0;right:-280px;width:260px;height:100vh;background:var(--bg2);border-left:1px solid var(--border);z-index:201;transition:right .25s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow-y:auto}.slide-panel.open{right:0}
.sp-hdr{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.sp-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',cursive;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--red2)}
.sp-close{background:none;border:none;color:var(--tx2);cursor:pointer;font-size:18px}
.sp-user{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:14px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.sp-av{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--bg4);border:1px solid var(--border2)}
.sp-uname{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px}.sp-uid{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3);letter-spacing:.5px}
.sp-links{padding:10px 8px;flex:1}
.sp-link{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 10px;border-radius:2px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--tx2);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.5px;transition:.15s;text-decoration:none}.sp-link:hover{background:var(--red-dim);color:var(--tx)}.sp-link.active{color:var(--red3)}
.sp-logout{margin:10px;padding:10px;background:rgba(192,57,43,.08);border:1px solid rgba(192,57,43,.2);border-radius:2px;color:var(--red2);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;display:block;transition:.15s;font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif}.sp-logout:hover{background:rgba(192,57,43,.2)}
#toast{position:fixed;bottom:20px;right:20px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:2px;padding:10px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.5px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px);transition:all .25s;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999}
#toast.show{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}#toast.success{border-color:rgba(192,57,43,.4);color:var(--red3)}#toast.error{border-color:rgba(255,50,50,.4);color:#ff6b6b}
@media(max-width:700px){.sidebar{transform:translateX(-100%)}.sidebar.mob-open{transform:translateX(0)}.main{margin-left:0}.hamburger{display:flex}.fr{grid-template-columns:1fr}.pg2{grid-template-columns:1fr}.add-row{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;grid-template-rows:auto auto}.add-row .btn-save{grid-column:1/-1}.lnav-links .lnav-link{display:none}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="landing" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:100vh">
  <nav class="lnav">
    <div class="lnav-logo">Sentrax<span>™</span></div>
    <div class="lnav-links">
      <a class="lnav-link" href="#features">Features</a>
      <a class="lnav-link" href="/auth/login">Login</a>
      <a class="lnav-btn" href="/auth/login">Open Dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid"></div>
    <div class="hero-badge">⚡ v8.4 — Live &amp; Protected</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">The<br/><span class="accent">Ultimate</span><br/>Discord Bot<span class="hero-tm">™</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Military-grade moderation, <strong>antinuke protection</strong>, economy, music, leveling and 200+ commands — all in one bot.</p>
    <a class="btn-hero" href="/auth/login">
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 0 0 .031.057 19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028c.462-.63.874-1.295 1.226-1.994a.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028 19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03z"/></svg>
      Enter Dashboard
    </a>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-val">200+</div><div class="hstat-lbl">Commands</div></div>
      <div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-val">99.9%</div><div class="hstat-lbl">Uptime</div></div>
      <div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-val">15+</div><div class="hstat-lbl">Protections</div></div>
      <div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-val">Free</div><div class="hstat-lbl">Always</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="feats" id="features">
    <div class="section-tag">Features</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Everything You Need</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Built for serious server owners. No compromises.</p>
    <div class="feat-grid">
      <div class="fc"><span class="fc-ico">☢️</span><div class="fc-name">Antinuke</div><div class="fc-desc">15+ real-time protections against raids, mass bans, channel deletions and server takeovers.</div></div>
      <div class="fc"><span class="fc-ico">🛡️</span><div class="fc-name">Automod</div><div class="fc-desc">Smart spam, invite, mention, caps, zalgo, phishing and custom bad word filtering.</div></div>
      <div class="fc"><span class="fc-ico">🎵</span><div class="fc-name">Music</div><div class="fc-desc">High quality Lavalink music with queue, filters, 24/7 mode and playlists.</div></div>
      <div class="fc"><span class="fc-ico">📈</span><div class="fc-name">Leveling</div><div class="fc-desc">XP system with rank cards, leaderboards, level-up roles and custom messages.</div></div>
      <div class="fc"><span class="fc-ico">💰</span><div class="fc-name">Economy</div><div class="fc-desc">Full economy with daily rewards, heists, fishing, mining and shops.</div></div>
      <div class="fc"><span class="fc-ico">⚖️</span><div class="fc-name">Moderation</div><div class="fc-desc">Ban, kick, warn, mute, purge, lockdown with full case and warning logging.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="flex:1"></div>
  <footer class="lfooter">
    <div class="lfooter-logo">Sentrax™</div>
    <div class="lfooter-copy">// © 2026 Sentrax. All rights reserved.</div>
